dc_description_s: This point data layer represents buildings for Portage County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Portage_Buildings_YE2016. [This file contains point data representing buildings placed based upon aerial photography. The points are attributed with address information with both County names and 911 ani/ali verified names. The points are also attributed with emergency service numbers and municipality.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
